  <data name="DirittoDiRecesso" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>&lt;h1&gt;
    Refund Policy
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;p class="par-index"&gt;
    &lt;b&gt;Rights of withdrawal and returns&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
    - You don't like the product that arrived, it's not the right size or has manufacturing defects?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
    Our returns and withdrawal policy states that if the customer is not 100% satisfied with any of the products ordered, we will be happy to
    refund it.&lt;br /&gt;
    - The customer can return the products within &lt;b&gt;14 calendar days&lt;/b&gt; of delivery of the package.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
    - The right of withdrawal is in any case subject to the following conditions: it applies to the product purchased in its entirety; the purchased good must be
    intact and returned in the original packaging, complete in all its parts; in accordance with the law, shipping costs are borne by the customer.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
    &lt;b&gt;The right of withdrawal&lt;/b&gt; is totally lost, due to the lack of the essential condition of integrity of the goods (packaging and its contents), in cases where Forrest
    ascertain the lack or non-integrity of the original packaging (original box) and/or recognize that the shoes have been worn outdoors.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
    In the event of a return for a defective product or a product different from the one ordered, we will send the courier to collect the return without any
    increased cost for the customer, once it has been ascertained that the defect is evident (via photos and videos) and not caused by the customer.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</value>
  </data>
  <data name="IstruzioniReso" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>&lt;h1 style="text-align:end"&gt;
     Return shipping instructions
 &lt;/h1&gt;
 &lt;br /&gt;
 &lt;p class="par-index " style=""&gt;
     &lt;b&gt;To exercise the right of return and/or withdrawal, follow these simple steps.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
     Contact Forrest on the &lt;b&gt;WhatsApp Support 24/7.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; link
     Pack the items in their original packaging.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
     Send the package to the following address: &lt;b&gt;Sartoria Forrest, Via Cupa Cesa n°2, 81030 Succivo CE&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
     We recommend using tracked shipping, as we assume no responsibility for returns lost or received late.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
     Once the return has been returned to the office, the goods will be examined to assess any damage or tampering, and if suitable, Forrest will refund the
     consumer the sum already paid solely and exclusively for the returned good.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
     The refund is made via PayPal or credit card within 14 days from the date of return of the goods, as per current legislation.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
 &lt;/p&gt;</value>
  </data>
  <data name="InformativaSpedizioni" xml:space="preserve">
