  <data name="TempiSpedizione" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>&lt;p class="par-index"&gt;
    &lt;b&gt;Shipping times&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
    Orders are shipped from Forrest, from Monday to Friday from 9:00 to 17:00.&lt;br /&gt;
    Orders received from 1pm on Friday, Saturday and Sunday will be shipped the following Monday.&lt;br /&gt;
    For available items, shipping will usually be made within 24/48 hours. You will receive your order within 5/7 working days from the moment of placing
    shipping.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
    &lt;b&gt;Traceability of shipment&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
    When the order is shipped, the courier in charge and Forrest will send customers information containing the shipping number and references
    tracking.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
    
    &lt;b&gt;Refund&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
    For prepaid goods (PayPal, Credit Card), with paid shipping that is returned to the office due to non-delivery or refused, a refund will be made
    exclusively the cost incurred by the customer for the purchase of the product and NOT the cost relating to its shipping.
&lt;/p&gt;</value>
  </data>
  <data name="SicurezzaPagamenti" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>&lt;h1 style="text-align:center"&gt;
    PAYMENTS AND PAYMENT SECURITY
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;p class="par-index " style=""&gt;
    The payment methods accepted on forrest.it are as follows:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
    Credit cards and prepaid cards registered with the PayPal circuit.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
    All transactions are processed via a secure server, guaranteeing customers maximum data protection.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
    By choosing the PayPal payment method, customers will be able to pay directly via their PayPal account.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
    Please check the address indicated on the account verified by Paypal and the relevant information on the site: https://www.paypal.com&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
    By bank transfer using the IBAN indicated in the «Your orders» section.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</value>
  </data>
